    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Group of several texts related to Islamic theological doctrine, mostly by or referencing Muḥammad ibn Yūsuf al-Sanūsī or Muḥammad al-Ṣāliḥ al-Awjalī; largely incomplete. The seventh work, by al-Awjalī, is incomplete and out of order. Contains some scribal errors and abbreviations which have been corrected or clarified by a later reader. Some texts contain extensive interlinear insertions, particularly the end of the 2nd work and the entire 7th work.The pages are loose leaves wrapped in a hide folder.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="546" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
